  <summary>2/8/2005--Introduced.
Urges the interim Government of Iraq to ensure: (1) that the charges brought against Saddam Hussein include charges for the crimes his government committed against the people of Iran during the 1980-1988 Iran-Iraq war, including the use of chemical weapons; and (2) a fair trial against Saddam Hussein.</summary>
